<h2><a name="introduction"></a>1. Introduction</h2>

<p>By default, OVA disables elements such as the timeline on the control bar during linear ad playback.</p>

<p>For <i>OVA for Flowplayer</i> it is possible to have fine grained control over which elements of the control bar are enabled/disabled during linear ad playback.</p>

<p>For <i>OVA for JW5</i>, if a Skin based control bar is used, fine grained control is also possible over the control bar. The standard JW5 control bar cannot be enabled/disabled this way.</p>

<h2><a name="example"></a>2. Working Example</h2>

<p>The following example illustrates how to disable all controls except the mute/volume button on the control bar.</p>

<!--- START OVA SPECIFIC HTML -->
<div id="ova-example-input" style="display:none;">
	<div id="ova-config" companion="false">
	{
          "player": {
             "modes": {
                "linear": {
                   "controls": { 
                      "enableFullscreen": false,
                      "enablePlay": false,
                      "enablePause": false,
                      "enableMute": true,
                      "enableVolume": true
                   }
                }
             }
          },
          "ads": {
             "schedule": [
                {
                   "position": "pre-roll",
                   "tag": "OVA_AD_TAG_LINEAR_STREAM_WITH_80x300_COMPANION"
                }
             ]
          },
          "debug": {
              "levels": "fatal, config, vast_template"
          }
	}
	</div>
	<div id="ova-flowplayer-config">
	{
	    "playlist": [
	        {
	           "url": "OVA_HTTP_SHOW_STREAM"
	        }
	    ],
	    "plugins": {
	        "controls": {
	           "autoHide": "never"
	        },
	        "ova": {
	           "url": "OVA_FLOWPLAYER_PLUGIN_SWF"
	        }
	    }
	}
	</div>
	<div id="ova-jw5-config" active="true">
	{
        "flashplayer": "OVA_JW5_PLAYER_SWF",
	    "playlist": [
	        {
	           "file": "OVA_HTTP_SHOW_STREAM"
	        }
	    ],
        "width": 450,
        "height": 300,
        "skin": "OVA_JW5_SKIN",
	    "controlbar": { "position": "bottom" },
	    "plugins": {
	    }
	}
	</div>
</div>
<div>
	<div>
		<h3>Embed code:</h3>
	</div>
	<div id="ova-example-output" style="">
